textAfterTable: 13 Songs Biography Genre: Electronic Years Active: '90s, '00s De/vision is a synth-pop band from Darmstadt, Germany, consisting of vocalist Steffen and keyboardists Thomas and Markus. The trio formed in 1988 and released several full-lengths, EPs, and remix albums.
